{"word":"G1246 - διακατελέγχομαι - diakatelénchomai - dee-ak-at-el-eng'-khom-ahee - Convince","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">διακατελέγχομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">diakatelénchomai</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">dee-ak-at-el-eng'-khom-ahee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Convince</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - சம்பாஷணை பண்ணு"},{"paragraph":"to confute with rivalry and effort or in a contest"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Middle voice from <a href=\"#/G1223 - διά - diá - dee-ah'/1223\">G1223</a> and a compound of <a href=\"#/G2596 - κατά - katá - kat-ah'/2596\">G2596</a> and <a href=\"#/G1651 - ἐλέγχω - elénchō - el-eng'-kho/1651\">G1651</a>; to <i>prove downright</i>, that is, <i>confute:</i> - convince.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}